headline: Capital Credit Union Modernizes Operations and Positions for Growth with Jack Henry
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) is pleased to announce that Capital Credit Union converted to Jack Henry's Symitar® platform and complementary products to support its future growth.
